title: Redick: Lakers must get in 'championship shape'

title: Are we set for Man Utd v Tottenham final in Europa League?
description: The odds are looking favourable for a sixth all-English European final, after Manchester United and Tottenham both win semi-final first legs on Thursday.

title: 'Nobody expected this' - was win in Bilbao best of Amorim's Man Utd reign?
description: Ruben Amorim said "nobody expected" Manchester United's win at Athletic Bilbao, but was it the best of his tenure so far?

title: Littler makes Premier League history by winning in Birmingham
description: Luke Littler captured a record fifth Premier league nightly win of the season in Birmingham as he defeated Michael van Gerwen to make more history.

title: Mainoo: EL triumph won't make Man Utd's season a success but would give hope
description: Manchester United midfielder Kobbie Mainoo has admitted winning the Europa League will not make the season a success but could provide a platform for the future.

title: Canyon's Addyson Bristow wins 1,600 to complete distance sweep at UIL state track meet
description: Canyon's Addyson Bristow completes distance sweep with victory in 1,600, after also winning 800, at UIL state championships.

title: Softball: Sooners outlast Florida in extra innings to open series
description: It looked like the Sooners would fall victim to missed opportunities at Florida on Thursday. The Sooners opened the extra frame with back-to-back-to-back singles from Ella Parker, Ailana Agbayani and Nelly McEnroe-Marinas, loading the bases with zero outs. Abby Dayton came to the plate and delivered an RBI single, giving the Sooners a one-run lead.
